.TH "megasas_alloc_ctrl_mem" 9 "megasas_alloc_ctrl_mem" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
megasas_alloc_ctrl_mem \- Allocate per controller memory for core data structures which are not common across MFI adapters and fusion adapters. For MFI based adapters, allocate producer and consumer buffers. For fusion adapters, allocate memory for fusion context.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" megasas_alloc_ctrl_mem
.BI "(struct megasas_instance *instance "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "instance" 12
Adapter soft state
.SH "RETURN"
0 for SUCCESS
